    "body": "I wasn't planing to add a placebo although my thinking my be naive here: z-sorting of effects is expensive https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/7520#issuecomment-75443959 so less effects improves performance. The question is probably where to draw the line: which effects are required for gameplay: removing corpses e.g. might cause some irritations etc. but if the whole plan won't make the game run smoother on less powerful hardware, then we don't need to pursue this further.\n"
