    "body": "That comment was based on outdated info and assumptions.  @RoosterDragon ran the numbers on recent code and found it to be cheap: #10119\n\n> Sorting just the actors alone costs 1.4% CPU, whilst sorting both actors and effects raises it to 1.8%. So the performance impact isn't too bad.\n"
